---
import SidebarLayout from '../../../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<SidebarLayout app="css">
  <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-5 text-custom-accent text-center">
    Responsive Design
  </h1>

  <section class="mb-5 space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-custom-secondary">
    <p>
      Responsive design ensures your website looks and functions well on all devices, from mobile phones to desktop computers. It's achieved through flexible layouts, media queries, and responsive units.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Media Queries</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`/* Mobile First Approach */
.container {
  padding: 1rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .container {
    padding: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
}

/* Common Breakpoints */
/* Small: 576px, Medium: 768px, Large: 992px, X-Large: 1200px */`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Responsive Units</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`/* Relative Units */
.container {
  /* Viewport units */
  width: 100vw;
  height: 100vh;
  
  /* Percentage */
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  
  /* Relative font units */
  font-size: 1rem; /* Based on root element */
  font-size: 1em; /* Based on parent element */
  
  /* Fluid typography */
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
}

/* Flexible images */
img {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mb-3">Responsive Strategies</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">Mobile First</strong>: Design for mobile, then enhance for larger screens</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">Fluid Layouts</strong>: Use percentages and max-width instead of fixed widths</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">Flexible Images</strong>: Ensure images scale appropriately</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">CSS Grid & Flexbox</strong>: Use modern layout methods for responsiveness</li>
        <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">Viewport Meta Tag</strong>: Essential for mobile responsiveness</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SidebarLayout>